%% Llama Stack - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.24/llama-stack.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Auth as Authentication MW<br/>(OAuth2 JWT)
    participant Quota as Quota MW<br/>(Rate Limiter)
    participant Tracing as Tracing MW<br/>(OpenTelemetry)
    participant Router as Inference Router<br/>(Routing Table)
    participant VLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant JWKS as JWKS Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OTEL as OTEL Collector<br/>4318/TCP HTTP
    participant SQLite as SQLite KV Store<br/>(Local)

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 1: Chat Completion via vLLM

    Client->>LS: POST /v1/inference/chat-completion<br/>Authorization: Bearer <JWT><br/>8321/TCP Optional TLS
    LS->>Auth: Validate Bearer Token
    Auth->>JWKS: GET /.well-known/jwks.json<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    JWKS-->>Auth: Public Keys (JWKS)
    Auth->>Auth: Verify JWT signature<br/>Validate audience/issuer<br/>Extract claims (sub, groups)
    Auth-->>LS: User principal + access_attributes

    LS->>Quota: Check rate limit
    Quota->>SQLite: Lookup client quota
    SQLite-->>Quota: Current count
    Quota-->>LS: Allowed (< 1000/day authenticated)

    LS->>Tracing: Create trace span
    Tracing->>OTEL: Export span start<br/>4318/TCP OTLP HTTP

    LS->>Router: Route inference request
    Router->>Router: Lookup model in routing table<br/>Resolve to vLLM provider
    Router->>VLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Authorization: Bearer <API_TOKEN>
    VLLM-->>Router: Completion Response (or SSE stream)
    Router-->>LS: Inference Result

    LS->>Tracing: Complete trace span
    Tracing->>OTEL: Export span end<br/>4318/TCP OTLP HTTP

    LS-->>Client: JSON Response / SSE Stream<br/>8321/TCP

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 2: Agent with RAG Tool Execution

    Client->>LS: POST /v1/agents<br/>8321/TCP (Create Agent)
    LS-->>Client: agent_id

    Client->>LS: POST /v1/agents/{id}/session<br/>8321/TCP (Create Session)
    LS-->>Client: session_id

    Client->>LS: POST /v1/agents/{id}/session/{sid}/turn<br/>8321/TCP (Execute Turn)

    LS->>Router: Agent turn execution
    Router->>Router: RAG Tool: Query vector store
    Note right of Router: FAISS (in-process)<br/>No network call

    Router->>VLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>8000/TCP (LLM inference with context)
    VLLM-->>Router: LLM Response

    Router->>Router: Safety Shield check<br/>(LlamaGuard in-process)

    Router-->>LS: Agent turn result
    LS-->>Client: Turn Response / SSE Stream

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 3: Telemetry Export

    LS->>Tracing: Collect traces & metrics
    Tracing->>OTEL: POST /v1/traces (OTLP)<br/>4318/TCP HTTP
    Tracing->>SQLite: Store traces locally<br/>(backup/query)
